  </info>

  <title>Remove a world clock</title>
  <p>If you no longer need one of your world clocks, you can delete it.</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Press the <gui style="button">World</gui> button.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Right click on the world clock of your choice. Alternatively, you
      can also press the button with a tick mark on the top right corner.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Mark all the world clocks you wish to delete by either clicking or
      right clicking on them.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press the <gui style="button">Delete</gui> button.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press the <gui style="button">Done</gui> button to finish.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <note style="info">
    <p>The <gui style="button">Delete</gui> button shows up only when you have
    marked at least one clock for deletion.</p>
  </note>

